[11/03/2017 13:24:22] <font color="#ffffff">¡Camping, camping...!</font>
[11/03/2017 13:24:26] <font color="#00ff00">Sí, sí, sí, sí. Camping total.</font>
[11/03/2017 13:24:28] <font color="#00ff00">Un camping total</font>
