[11/03/2017 15:38:35] <font color="#00ff00">"Saber y ganar",</font>
[11/03/2017 15:38:39] <font color="#00ff00">un programa presentado</font>
[11/03/2017 15:38:39] <font color="#00ff00">por Jordi Hurtado.</font>
